a determinative, but \uc0\u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258  shows what the word means.\
\
This ancient text continues--\'93Come thou to me, glorified and purified;\
let thy hands [_here the text is obliterated_], shine thou with thine\
head (\uc0\u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 ). Give me my mouth that I may speak with it,\
and guide me on the glorious roads which are in heaven.\'94\
\
The Turin text is very corrupt, and parts of it are incapable of\
translation.\
\
1. \uc0\u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 .\
