                             CHAPTER XXXVI.\
\
              _Chapter whereby the \uc0\u256 pshait is kept back._\
\
\
Away from me, thou with parted lips! I am Chnemu, the Lord of Shennu,\
who am bringing the words of the gods to R\uc0\u257 . And I announce the news to\
Nebes.\
\
