connects the Eye with the opening of the year.\
\
The priestly title \uc0\u8258 \u8258 \u8258 , \'91holder of the Eye,\'92 is like all such\
titles, that of the divinity whom the priest personates. The god himself\
is hieroglyphically represented by the sign \uc0\u8258 \u8258  of an ape holding\
the Eye.\
\
23. _The tunnels_, \uc0\u8258 \u8258 \u8258 , \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 , Teta, 291;\
