\f0  Cepheus) in the immediate neighbourhood of the Polar Star\
which represented Osiris. On the ancient coffins of Amamu and Sit-Bastit\
there is a chapter[87] for assuming the form of a Vulture \uc0\u8258 \u8258 \u8258 ,\
in which the speaker says \'93I am the Vulture god who is on the\
\uc0\u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 .\'94\
