\uc0\u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258  said of Osiris on the\
stel\'e6 of the twelfth dynasty, the constellation in heaven and not a\
place at Abydos was meant.\
