\uc0\u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258  in the title of 137B. The Ammon Ritual has\
\uc0\u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258  _strike a Light_. Dr. von Lemm thinks\
that by a play of words it is implied not only that a light but Sut is\
struck.\
