\uc0\u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258  _in Abydos, Aa_ and _Petamenemapt_.\
\
3. _Riseth up_ \uc0\u8258 , _Ba_, \u8258 \u8258  _Marseilles_;\
\uc0\u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258  _Aa_, \u8258 \u8258  _Petamenemapt_.\
\
4. _Opposition_ \uc0\u8258 \u8258 \u8258 , where \u8258  is = \u8258  as in the Sallier\
Calendar. The sense is made clear in the parallel passages\
\uc0\u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 \u8258 . \u8258 , if not an error of recent\
transcribers, is a wrong reading for \uc0\u8258 , which is very distinctly\
